caption.text:
Adoring her since the first time her photo came up in my instagram explore. It was 2015 and since that time, I was inspired not only by her fashion style, her achievements, or anything exposed obviously in the social media. More than that, she has been inspiring me by the way she lives her life. I have talked to her 'directly' when I shamelessly texted her through Line just to thank her of how inspiring she is for me and sending her the warm prayer and love because I just thought she deserves it. And, unbelieveably she replied my Line and thanked me back and giving some positive words. See how humble she is, omg!
In that conversation, I told her that one day we should meet and she said 'wish we could meet someday'. So this is the one chance I take, to meet a woman who has been inspiring me so much.  I have bought my ticket also, from Bandung to Yogyakarta just to meet, get more inspired, and thank her directly. I just can't wait for that day in #lolyk #lolykcelebration #lolykcelebration

It was yesterday when I met him. Unsupposed and unpredicted but i believe, destined. On Argo Parahyangan earliest train from Bandung to Gambir. Many things he told me and I learned so much from him. Dia bahkan nganterin aku sampai ketemu ojeg untuk menuju MGK Kemayoran. Beliau minta maaf tidak bisa antar aku ke MGK karena harus sholat dhuha dulu di Gambir. Tapi di anterin sampe dapet ojeg saja udah more than enough for me. I said nothing but thank you in the end and he offer me to come to his house and discuss many things since he has a youngest daughter at my age. Penampilannya yang sederhana banget bikin saya gak nyangka kalau ternyata beliau adalah Pak Bambang Adi Pratignjo, Direktur Teknik PT Kereta Api Indonesia Commuter Jabodetabek 2009-2013. I can now say that he is one of the great men Indonesia ever have.
